The paper proposes an extension of Answer Set Programming (ASP) to deal with partial functions, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the treatment of equality in ASP, which is a topic related to logic (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper presents a practical application of the proposed extension, which is related to computational logic (cs.CL) and databases (cs.DB).
